# MixTV environment example
# Runtime secrets are stored in the EdgeOne env KV namespace, not in .env files.

# EdgeOne Pages KV bindings are fixed in code:
# - env: runtime server config records, including AUTH_SECRET, USERNAME,
#   PASSWORD, and CRON_BASE_URL.
# - cfg: admin/site/video-source config records.
# - cache: cache/stat records.
# - user: playback progress, favorites, watch history, and search history.
